Items.Name: High Technology Control - NSW
Items.Description:
High Technology Control is an Australian company established since 1985 harbouring many years of experience within the electrical industry. As an Authorised Value Provider for ABB, a worldwide leader in the Power Quality, Automation and Control Industry, HTC can offer products, services and support of the highest quality. In collaboration with Schneider Electric, as the Authorised Cooling Partner, HTC serves the cooling market providing a range of precision cooling products supported by world renowned expertise. As the sole agent in Australia for Fagor Automation, BEI Encoders and Glentek Servo Systems, our engineers have the expertise to offer fast service without compromising quality. Through these network alliances HTC has access to a wide range of low voltage products and is able to provide high quality products at competitive prices within the market.

HTC aims to be the most trusted provider within the industry by developing and maintaining customer relationships.

This commitment has enhanced the company’s profile allowing for a national footprint and continual long term growth.

Items.Description:
INGEAL S.A. Tenemos cerca de 32 años, y hoy somos el Integrador en Infraestructura para Data Centers Sostenibles más completos del mercado, con tecnología de punta y de mayor experiencia en Colombia.
Nuestro portafolio de clientes nos lo confirma: Somos la compañía que más experiencia y conocimiento aporta en Diseño, Venta, Implementación, Manejo y Soporte de Centros de Datos en nuestro país. Contamos con el respaldo y distribución directa de las fábricas más prestigiosas en nuestro “Business Core”.
Somos miembros activos de las más importantes asociaciones del medio que son referentes en Colombia y en el Mundo como: ASHRAE, ACAIRE, BICSI, AFCOM, 7X24, THE GREEN GRID, e IEEE. Hemos logrado las certificaciones más exigentes ISO 9001, ISO 14001 y OSHAS 18001 y ofrecemos hoy a nuestros clientes la más alta calidad en nuestros procesos y normas.
